      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主框架：Idle复合状态包含Ready，Processing复合状态包含Validating、Queued和Running。Running再嵌套Initializing、Executing、Finalizing。Paused作为独立状态，内部有WaitingResume指向Timeout。",
